message: "In Georgia, the operation resulted in the recovery of seven child victims and four adult victims, along with the arrest of three pimps or traffickers."

data.description: An FBI-led investigation that led to 11 victims of sex trafficking being rescued statewide also resulted in the arrest of three men in Smyrna who now face pimping charges, authorities
data.title: FBI operation recovers 11 sex trafficking victims, arrests three on pimping charges in Smyrna
